fish_help_method:
The DO levels in the morning were very low at 1.5 and there was also Ammonia detected in the water sample, we immediately informed the farmer and asked him to do water exchange, stop feeding for 48 hours and use zeolite.
Farmer implemented the prescribed corrective actions and during our follow up visit the DO levels came back to normal ranges and there was no traces of Ammonia found in the water sample.

name: Chandu
corrective_actions_taken:
Water exchange
Turning aerators on for 2 days
Godrej DE-AM for Ammonia
corrective_actions_outcome: Ammonia levels came to 0 and DO levels are back in the required range
corrective_actions_farmer_ease: Easy. I implemented them immediately and without financial or other difficulties.
fish_help_method:
The Ammonia levels in the water were high and few dead fish were being observed everyday, the DO levels in the water were also low.
We have recommended to turn on the aerators for 2 days and stop feeding and use zeolite for reducing ammonia. Farmer used Godrej DE-AM instead of Zeolite.
After two follow-up visits the ammonia levels reduced to 0 and DO levels were back in required range.
